response.original_title: Joey Page: The Last Night Before Lockdown
response.overview: Nobody would choose to record their comedy special an hour after the PM said “Stay At Home”…would they? Recorded exclusively for NextUp on the evening of the 16th of March 2020, South Londoner Joey Page brings all the faded glitz, Walkers crisps and home made costumes he can muster for this hour of daft delights on 80’s nostalgia, being banned from Greggs, and the death knoll that is turning 31.
response.title: Joey Page: The Last Night Before Lockdown
